overview: April 20, 2017, MGM Television announced that Mark Burnett, MGM's President, Television Group and Digital, and Jeanie Buss formed a partnership to develop new content across a range of unscripted programming and digital formats for WOW!. Its fifth season commenced production in Los Angeles on October 2018, with its live event at the historic Belasco Theater in Los Angeles.
title: Women Of Warriors VI
